\begin_layout Standard
As we said the rings contact points must satisfy delta-coupling condition.
 For (j-1)-th to j-th ring contact coupling conditions are following:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula $\psi_{j-1}(\pi)=\psi_{j}(0)=\psi$
\end_inset


